> This was caused due to `Release: <CI_CNT>.<B_CNT>` in the OBS project config. I'll check on how best to fix this..

Alright, so I changed ^ to `Release: <SPEC_REL>` as per OBS' advice, which will create rpms with the exact release tag as specified in the spec file. That should hopefully fix this issue.

@cranebytes please try installing in a few minutes, you should see `conmon-2.0.16-3` on the OBS repo.
